  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This pilot study is using a novel technology to measure the rate of turnover of new fat
      cells. Analysis of volunteer samples is ongoing, however the study is currently not enrolling
      new volunteers.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
